Name: ParkTo
About the game: ParkTo is a simple puzzle game that stops the car at its destination. You don't drive a car yourself. The car just moves forward'. Use the given triggers to move the car to its destination: LEFT, RIGHT, STOP, BACKWARD, etc. Triggers can be placed on the path of the car or used on the car itself. FEATURES 48 handcrafted levels. Various trigger interactions reflecting car movements. Comfortable colors and minimal graphics. You can play without a driving license!
